{"tid":330512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球首宗！葛量洪醫院染日本腦炎病人因輸血中招","createTime":"2017-07-21T09:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T10:16:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8044b2ff3c38db13b6e2ff1a02550633a7e65e","tid":330512,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"一名5月初於瑪麗醫院接受換肺的病人，同月轉到葛量洪醫院留醫；直至本月6日接受輸血後，出現發燒及神志不清等病徵，昨日證實感染日本腦炎，情況危殆。據了解，紅十字會已驗出輸予該病人的血液中，有一包有日本腦炎病毒，是全球首宗，而有關的捐血人士也有捐出血小板、血漿，紅十字會仍會追蹤有相關血小板、血漿的去向。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總感染控制主任曾艾壯昨表示，文獻沒有記載透過輸血或器官移植感染日本腦炎的病例，但理論上有風險。<br />\n<br />\n防護中心表示，日本腦炎主要經蚊傳播，海外有科學文獻顯示，其他類似黃病毒，輸血和器官移植也可能傳播日本腦炎病毒。按現階段掌握病人的臨床紀錄及接觸史，仍需繼續流行病學調查，以盡量確認感染源頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56985042&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56985042%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170721&d=lQxHVXYVGApsbYdR3oXkxviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b86f58bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56985042%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170721&h=999132db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56985042&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170721</a>"},{"pid":"c8d75d575c56bc2f0296bacba8edffebbe1bbdb3","tid":330512,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"連登仔不應該發起不捐血運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢條友幾傑出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4146e2e729e7a9f6690136fe3369564a91421a98","tid":330512,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:34:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4ff2e02c2bdead896ce5dd9160d25d50d086813","tid":330512,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港衝出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}